                                Companies are increasingly turning to advanced solutions that automate the capture of all interactions and activities, seamlessly integrating them into CRM systems.
                            </p>
                        
                            
                            <p class="current_issue_article_title">
                                <a id="MainContentPlaceHolder_rptArticles_lnkArticleTitle_2" href="https://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/Web-Exclusives/Viewpoints/How-CSOs-Can-Maximize-Sales-Analytics-Impact-163691.aspx">How CSOs Can Maximize Sales Analytics’ Impact</a>
