                                This approach aims not just to engage customers but to envelop them in the narrative and values of a brand.
                            </p>
                        
                            
                            <p class="current_issue_article_title">
                                <a id="MainContentPlaceHolder_rptArticles_lnkArticleTitle_4" href="https://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/Web-Exclusives/Viewpoints/Its-Time-to-Make-AI-More-Human-163561.aspx">It’s Time to Make AI More Human</a>
