                            </p>
                        
                            
                            <p class="current_issue_article_title">
                                <a id="MainContentPlaceHolder_rptArticles_lnkArticleTitle_14" href="https://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/Web-Exclusives/Viewpoints/Prepare-In-Store-Employees-for-Tough-Shoppers-and-Situations-162763.aspx">Prepare In-Store Employees for Tough Shoppers and Situations</a>
