                            <p class="current_issue_article_title">
                                <a id="MainContentPlaceHolder_rptArticles_lnkArticleTitle_17" href="https://www.destinationcrm.com/Articles/Web-Exclusives/Viewpoints/Generative-AI-Will-Redefine-Crucial-Work-Skills-but-It-Cant-Replace-Human-Expertise-162574.aspx">Generative AI Will Redefine Crucial Work Skills, but It Can’t Replace Human Expertise</a>
